            "reviews": "“It feels really satisfying... Very simple yet satisfying mechanic.”<br><a href=\"https://youtu.be/FN4md820hhg?t=48\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Jonas Tyroller</a><br><br>“A simple, yet fun arcade game. [...] Another case of a simple idea doing a lot when you get down to it.  Brilliant fun, do check it out.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.gamingonlinux.com/articles/ghost-grab-3000-is-a-very-satisfying-arcade-game-where-you-chain-ghosts-together.15379\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GamingOnLinux</a><br><br>“Ghost Grab 3000 is blessed with incredible polish for a very simple idea.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.bonusstage.co.uk/2020/07/07/ghost-grab-3000-review/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Bonus Stage</a><br>",
